room_title: Escape room "Sherlock Holmes" by Axxiom Escape Rooms Rehoboth in Rehoboth Beach
room_description: The title speaks for itself! It will take multiple detectives to solve the mystery of this exodus. Built around the English theme of the great Sherlock Holmes, this Exodus has a nostalgic presence that anyone can appreciate. This escape room utilizes multiple puzzles, clues, and mysteries to send you into a permanent state of confusion.
